{"description":"The previous project excited me so much that I set myself to explore the different possibilities of organizing a small space...","body":"<p>The “<a href=\"/portfolio/yummy-green\">Yummy green</a>“ studio seemed like the perfect subject for the exercise, since I already had a solution for it.</p>\n<p>I greatly admire modern Scandinavian (interior) design, not only for its ability to blend beauty and creativity with practicality, but also for its sheer boldness. I took inspiration from it when I designed this layout that displays a regular bed. IKEA’s Kivik sofa, with its small, one person modules is a great choice for narrow places and the stool can be used as either a seat or a table. The wardrobe, media center and other storage cabinets have been combined in one large, compact wall unit, while the balcony has been turned into a private play-and-work space. The parapet separating the balcony from the rest of the room received a tabletop for meals or drinks. Additional storage can be found underneath the bed.</p>\n<p>Dominated by white, northern interiors, particularly Swedish, are pigmented with bright, saturated colors and large texture prints. It’s a great way to turn your living space from dull to exciting and inspirational.</p>\n<div class=\"pics\">\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 1\" title=\"Picture 1\" src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-1-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-1-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-1-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-1-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"northern-odyssey-picture-1.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 2\" title=\"Picture 2\" src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-2-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-2-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-2-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-2-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"northern-odyssey-picture-2.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 3\" title=\"Picture 3\" src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-3-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-3-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-3-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-3-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"northern-odyssey-picture-3.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 4\" title=\"Picture 4\" src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-4-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-4-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-4-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-4-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"northern-odyssey-picture-4.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 5\" title=\"Picture 5\" src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-5-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-5-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-5-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-5-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"northern-odyssey-picture-5.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 6\" title=\"Picture 6\" src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-6-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-6-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-6-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-6-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"northern-odyssey-picture-6.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 7\" title=\"Picture 7\" src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-7-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-7-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-7-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-7-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"northern-odyssey-picture-7.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 8\" title=\"Picture 8\" src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-8-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-8-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-8-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/northern-odyssey-picture-8-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"northern-odyssey-picture-8.jpg\"></div>\n</div>\n","gallery":["northern-odyssey-picture-1.jpg","northern-odyssey-picture-2.jpg","northern-odyssey-picture-3.jpg","northern-odyssey-picture-4.jpg","northern-odyssey-picture-5.jpg","northern-odyssey-picture-6.jpg","northern-odyssey-picture-7.jpg","northern-odyssey-picture-8.jpg"]}